column5: anyone stay at crystal harbour resort near sioux narrows.. thinking of staying for the night before our trip.thanks
Clean rooms, nothing fancy and great food.
agree with Darcy, just don't order cocktail, drink bear or a simple mixed drink, we got charged for the mix in a manhatten!
